original: Light blue shoulder tape with a patch of United Nations troops in Chernarus.

english: Blue shoulder tape with Trade Union print. It does not guarantee the credibility of the wearer.
czech: Modrá páska přes rameno s potiskem Obchodní unie. Nezaručuje důvěryhodnost nositele.

original: Green shoulder tape with National Party applique. Long live Chernarus!
english: Green shoulder tape with National Party applique. Sláva Černarusi!
czech: Zelená páska přes rameno s nášivkou Národní Strany. Ať žije Černarus!

original: Red shoulder tape with a patch of the Chernarussian Movement of Red Star.
english: Red armband with a patch of the Chernarussian Movement of Red Star.
czech: Rudá páska přes rameno s nášivkou Černaruského hnutí Rudé hvězdy.

original: Shoulder tape in the colors of the Republic of Poland's flag.
english: Shoulder tape in the colors of the Republic of Poland's flag
czech: Páska přes rameno v barvách Polské republiky.

original: This shoulder tape holds a memory of a beloved comrade survivor from Czechia. A pioneer of altruistic RP, not a selfish man, we've lost on our way. Long live Jack Forest! Shall his name be remembered by the new blood!
english: This shoulder tape holds a memory of a beloved comrade survivor from Czechia. A pioneer of altruistic RP, not a selfish man, we've lost on our way. Long live Jack Forest! Shall his name be remembered by the new blood!
czech: Ztracená páska přes rameno s mužským jménem. Kde je Jack?

original: Black shoulder tape. Who are Bren's Ravens? I'm in fear!
english: Black shoulder tape. Who are Bren's Ravens? I'm in fear!
czech: Páska přes rameno. Kdo jsou Brenovy Havrani? Mám strach!

original: Tape over the shoulder of the Chernarussian Patriotic Union. Glory to the New Republic!
english: Tape over the shoulder of the Chernarussian Patriotic Union. Glory to the New Republic!
czech: Páska přes rameno Vlastenecké Unie. Sláva Nové Republice!

original: Tape over the shoulder of the Novy Sobor Militia. Bow to your knees!
english: Tape over the shoulder of the Novy Sobor Militia. Bow to your knees!
czech: Páska přes rameno Novosoborské Milice. Klaňte se ke kolenou!

original: You know, I am kind of a priest myself ...
english: You know, I am kind of a priest myself ...
czech: Víte, taky jsem tak trochu kněz ...
Páska přes rameno koaličního spolku na území Kamenky a okolí.

original: Ordinary black denim jacket. It looks cool, ideal for breaking women's hearts.
english: Ordinary black denim jacket. It looks cool, ideal for breaking women's hearts.
czech: Obyčejná černá džínová bunda. Vypadá cool, perfektní na lámání ženských srdcí.

original: Black denim jacket with a print of the Russian rock band KINO and a picture of Viktor Tsoy.
english: Black denim jacket with a print of the Russian rock band KINO and a picture of Viktor Tsoy.
czech: Černá džínová bunda s potiskem ruské rockové skupiny KINO a obrázkem Viktora Tsoje.

original: Blue denim jacket with a picture of the Slovak band Team.
english: Blue denim jacket with a picture of the Slovak band Team.
czech: Modrá džínová bunda s obrázkem slovenské kapely Team.

original: Blue denim jacket with a picture of the Slovak legend - Paul Nabera.
english: Blue denim jacket with a picture of the Slovak legend - Paul Nabera.
czech: Modrá džínová bunda s obrázkem slovenské legendy Paľa Nabery.

original: Combat pants used by many military factions. They are comfortable and durable against damage by friction.
english: Combat pants used by many military factions. They are comfortable and durable against damage by friction.
czech: Bojové kalhoty, které využívá mnoho vojenských organizací. Tyto kalhoty jsou odolné proti poškození způsobenému třením.

original: Police jacket in the urban pattern of the Kamysh OREL intervention unit.
english: Police jacket in the urban pattern of the Kamysh OREL intervention unit.
czech: Policejní bunda ve městském vzoru Kamysh zásahové jednotky OREL.

original: Black Uniform of the Chernarussian Police Department. It probably does not suit any purpose anymore, but you wouldn't want to be found wearing one, in presence of real officer.
english: Black Uniform of the Chernarussian Police Department. It probably does not suit any purpose anymore, but you wouldn't want to be found wearing one, in presence of real officer.
czech: Černá policejní bunda Černaruského policejního sboru. Dost pravděpodobně již neplní svůj účel, ale nebylo by nejlepší být v ní spatřen někým, kdo u policie sloužil.

original: Black Police Pants of the Chernarussian Police Department. They're well insulated and offer some degree of protection against the rain, however they'll get wet after some time.
english: Black Police Pants of the Chernarussian Police Department. They're well insulated and offer some degree of protection against the rain, however they'll get wet after some time.
czech: Černé policejní kalhoty Černaruského policejního sboru. Jsou dobře izolované a nabízí určitý stupeň nepromokavosti, po délší chvíli však promoknou.

original: Black beret. Used mainly by security forces.
english: Black beret. Used mainly by security forces.
czech: Černý baret. Využíván především bezpečnostními sbory.

original: A can of lemonade with a high sugar content. Imported from the Czech Republic.
english: A can of lemonade with a high sugar content. Imported from the Czech Republic.
czech: Plechovka limonády s vysokým obsahem cukru. Importováno z České republiky.

original: A can of Panzer Beer beer. Classic recipe since 2008
english: A can of Panzer Beer beer. Classic recipe since 2008
czech: Plechovka s pivem značky Panzer Beer. Klasická receptura od roku 2008

original: A can of Kozlov beer. This beer has been brewed in Chernarus since 1895 and holds a name of the great warrior, that once ruled Chernarus - The Great Ivan Kozlov.
english: A can of Kozlov beer. This beer has been brewed in Chernarus since 1895 and holds a name of the great warrior, that once ruled Chernarus - The Great Ivan Kozlov.
czech: Plechovka s pivem značky Kozlov. Toto pivo bylo vařeno v regionu již od roku 1895. Pivo zároveň nese jméno jednoho z velkých středověkých vůdců z regionu - Ivana Kozlova z dynastie Kozlovů.
Plechovka s kvasem značky Rasputin Kvass.

original: Can with yeast of Bardak liqueur.
english: Can with yeast of Bardak liqueur.
czech: Plechovka s kvasem likérky Bardak a syn.

original: Hiking pants with a local favorite fairy tale character - Mole.
english: Hiking pants with a local favorite fairy tale character - Mole.
czech: Turistické kalhoty s místní oblíbenou pohádkovou postavou - Krtečkem.

original: Police pants in the urban Kamysh camo pattern of OREL intervention unit.
english: Police pants in the urban Kamysh camo pattern of OREL intervention unit.
czech: Policejní kalhoty ve městském vzoru Kamysh zásahové jednotky OREL.

original: A reflective police vest is a symbol of hopelessness for road pirates. In any case, we advise you to always stop.
english: A reflective police vest is a symbol of hopelessness for road pirates. In any case, we advise you to always stop.
czech: Reflexní policejní vesta je symbolem beznaděje pro piráty silnic. Každopádně radíme vždy zastavit.

original: Woop ti di scoop di poop. Woop ti di scoopti, woop di scoop. Scoop di di woop ti, scoop. Woop.
english: Woop ti di scoop di poop. Woop ti di scoopti, woop di scoop. Scoop di di woop ti, scoop. Woop.
czech: Dávám celý dny itemy lidem a jediný, co z toho mám je takhle vesta!

original: Classic black police vest. Its advantage is thick plates, which do not stop high-caliber ammunition so well, but it can minimalize knife attack wounds.
english: Classic black police vest. Its advantage is thick plates, which do not stop high-caliber ammunition so well, but it can minimalize knife attack wounds.
czech: Klasická černá policejní vesta. Její výhodou jsou silné pláty, které sice nezastaví tak dobře vysokorážní munici, ale útok nožem ano.

original: Classical black anti-stab police vest with a Militia logo. Its advantage is thick plates, which do not stop high-caliber ammunition so well, but can minimalize knife attack wounds.
english: Classical black anti-stab police vest with a Militia logo. Its advantage is thick plates, which do not stop high-caliber ammunition so well, but can minimalize knife attack wounds.
czech: Klasická černá policejní vesta s insignií Milice. Její výhodou jsou silné pláty, které sice nezastaví tak dobře vysokorážní munici, ale útok nožem ano.

original: Athletic shoes from the Adios brand - The first choice of Chernarussian athletes. These comfortable shoes will make it easier for you to escape from all threats.
english: Athletic shoes from the Adios brand - The first choice of Chernarussian athletes. These comfortable shoes will make it easier for you to escape from all threats.
czech: Atletické boty od značky Adios - První volba černaruských atletů. Tyto pohodlné boty vám usnadní útěk před všemi hrozbami. Spěchej pomalu!

original: Radio requiring a 9V battery and cassette for its operation. The classic radio used to work, but the antenna is broken. The lovely tones of the built-in cassette player make work easier and fun.
english: Radio requiring a 9V battery and cassette for its operation. The classic radio used to work, but the antenna is broken. The lovely tones of the built-in cassette player make work easier and fun.
czech: Rádio vyžadující 9V baterii a kazetu ke svému provozu. Dříve fungovalo i klasické rádio, ale anténa je rozbitá. Líbezné tóny vestavěného kazeťáku usnadňují práci a baví.

original: Special sound device for emitting intense sound at higher frequencies by blowing air out of the human lungs. It can serve as a children's toy, a special musical instrument, signaling equipment, sports equipment, an aid for training animals, etc.
english: Special sound device for emitting intense sound at higher frequencies by blowing air out of the human lungs. It can serve as a children's toy, a special musical instrument, signaling equipment, sports equipment, an aid for training animals, etc.
czech: Speciální zvukové zařízení pro vydávání intenzivního zvuku o vyšších frekvencích pomocí vyfukování vzduchu z lidských plic. Může sloužit jako dětská hračka, speciální hudební nástroj, signalizační zařízení, sportovní náčiní, pomůcka pro výcvik zvířat apod.
